text: Of ðam lytlan hlawan to þan longan snapan on ða stræte forþ æfter strete oð cume to þan readan acon & ðær ðwers ofer ða wuda þæt cyme in pire broces heafde.
& æfter pire broc ðæt hit gæþ in bliðe up æfter bliþe oð hit cyme in ceabbe broc æfter broce þæt cume in ðan forde.
From ðan forde æfter þære strete þeligeð cumb welle lea oð cume on þa grene wege & forð æfter grene wege oð hit cymeþ æft to ðan lytlan lauwan.
Ðus hit hæfde eadelm & ælfred & æþelwold swa swa <hit> Wulfsige ðe blaca & æscbryht hit geærdeden heom.
